        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(proxy): apply enhanced NO_PROXY matching to global undici dispatcher (fixes #95998)",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes #95998.\n\nWhen `HTTPS_PROXY` is set, the global EnvHttpProxyAgent routes ALL requests through the proxy — including internal plugin requests that should bypass via `NO_PROXY`. The built-in undici NO_PROXY matcher does not support leading-dot subdomain patterns, CIDR notation, or octet wildcards.\n\nOpenClaw already has `matchesNoProxy()` that handles these — but it was only used by provider helpers, not the global dispatcher.\n\n## Changes Made\n\n1. **NO_PROXY-aware proxy dispatcher** — Wraps every EnvHttpProxyAgent with a Proxy that checks `matchesNoProxy()` before dispatching. Bypassed requests are routed through a direct Agent with the same timeout and connect policy.\n\n2. **Lifecycle synchronization (P1 fix)** — Promise-style `close()`/`destroy()` now **await** both the bypass agent AND the proxy dispatcher before settling. Previously the bypass agent was invoked fire-and-forget, so awaited global dispatcher shutdown could complete before bypass sockets were drained.\n\n3. **Timeout/connect consistency** — `forceResetGlobalDispatcher` now passes `connect` options to the bypass agent, matching other construction paths.\n\n## Evidence\n\n**Unit tests (35 tests):**\n```\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  35 passed (35)\n```\n\n**CIDR and octet-wildcard support (undici built-in v8.5.0 lacks these):**\n```\n=== Enhanced NO_PROXY matcher ===\n\n  ✅ CIDR: 100.64.0.0/10 match: matchesNoProxy=true\n  ✅ CIDR: outside range: matchesNoProxy=false\n  ✅ CIDR: 169.254.0.0/16 match: matchesNoProxy=true\n  ✅ CIDR: 169.254.0.0/16 no match: matchesNoProxy=false\n  ✅ Octet wildcard: 100.100.*.*: matchesNoProxy=true\n  ✅ Octet wildcard: no match: matchesNoProxy=false\n  ✅ Subdomain: bucket.cos.myqcloud.com (.myqcloud.com): match=true\n  ✅ Subdomain: api.openai.com (.myqcloud.com): match=false\n```\n\n**Real proxy live proof:**\n```\n=== Without NO_PROXY ===\n  [proxy] CONNECT httpbin.org:443 → through proxy ✅\n\n=== NO_PROXY.myqcloud.com ===\n  COS domain → 0 proxy connections (bypassed) ✅\n\n=== Non-matching domain ===\n  api.openai.com → through proxy (35 CONNECTs) ✅\n```\n\n## AI Assistance\n\n- AI-assisted: Yes",
